.SH NAME
grafana\-util\-change\-promotion\-preflight \- build a staged promotion review handoff from a source bundle and target inventory.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B grafana-util change promotion-preflight [\fIOPTIONS\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
build a staged promotion review handoff from a source bundle and target inventory.
.PP
when you are preparing a promotion review and want an explicit mapping and availability view.
.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
build a staged promotion review handoff from a source bundle and target inventory.
.EX
